            key in the provided page.
        </description>
        <name>escapeProperty</name>
        <function-class>com.demoorg.demo.wcm.tags.functions.UtilityFunctions</function-class>
        <function-signature>
            java.lang.String escapeProperty( com.day.cq.wcm.api.Page, java.lang.String )
        </function-signature>
