            page.  If the property is not set, true is returned.
        </description>
        <name>showFooter</name>
        <function-class>com.demoorg.demo.wcm.tags.functions.UtilityFunctions</function-class>
        <function-signature>
            boolean showFooter( com.day.cq.wcm.api.Page )
        </function-signature>
    </function>
    
    <function>
        <description>
